12 year's allocation for the child increased by the index factor;
13 (11) "Allocation for a student with a level four disability," for the school fiscal year
14 beginning July 1, 2025, is $18,053.89. For each school year thereafter, the
15 allocation for a student with a level four disability must be the previous fiscal year's
16 allocation for the child increased by the index factor;
17 (12) "Allocation for a student with a level five disability," for the school fiscal year
18 beginning July 1, 2025, is $37,039.28. For each school year thereafter, the
