28 (18) "Statewide local need," the amount of money required to provide special education
29 or special education and related services in this state, as calculated by adding
30 together:
31 (a) The sum of local need of each school district in this state, calculated
32 pursuant to subdivision (7);
33 (b) The amount set aside for extraordinary expenses, as defined in § 13-37-
34 40; and
